data.description: Beautiful country living just a 15 minute drive to Heber Springs Park, Greers Ferry Lake & More! This one level home features new fixtures throughout, new paint, a remodeled guest and primary bath with a jetted tub, new vinyl plank floors, new windows & more! Roof replaced in 2018 & Water Heater is less than 5 years old. Brand new stove to be installed. Come see this turn key home nestled on a beautiful, shaded lot with a fenced in backyard. New survey will be needed prior to closing. Agents See Remarks.
